race.description: Inglis Ready2race Sale Tomorrow Maiden Plate
race.comment: PEACE BIRD (13) came from last on straightening to grab fourth in an eye-catching debut over 1100m at Canterbury last time out. Capable of featuring in the finish over the extra 100m today with that race experience on board. FERNWEH (4) battled on fairly for a moderate fifth first-up in the same race as PEACE BIRD at Canterbury. Worth another chance with added fitness over a little more ground. SERPICO (10) wasn't all that far away when resuming over today's journey at Kembla recently. Placed over 1200m here second-up last prep so worth each-way consideration. A couple of first starters in NITRO (6) and BUGATTE (2) should attract plenty of interest. Both hail from leading yards and turned in their best trials to date at their latest appearances. Keep a close eye on the betting surrounding this duo.
